  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_013_000003",
    "sentence": "趙郡王琛，字永寶，高祖之弟也。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "趙郡",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_013_000004",
    "sentence": "少時便弓馬，有志氣。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_013_000005",
    "sentence": "高祖既匡天下，中興初，授散騎常侍、鎮西將軍、金紫光祿大夫。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "將軍",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 19,
        "end": 21
      },
      {
        "text": "大夫",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 26,
        "end": 28
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_013_000006",
    "sentence": "既居禁衛，恭勤慎密，率先左右。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_013_000007",
    "sentence": "太昌初，除車騎大將軍、左光祿大夫，封南趙郡公，食邑五千戶。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "大將軍",
