        "end": 16
      },
      {
        "text": "封南趙郡",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 17,
        "end": 21
      },
      {
        "text": "食邑",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 23,
        "end": 25
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_013_000008",
    "sentence": "尋拜驃騎大將軍、特進、開府儀同三司、散騎常侍。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "大將軍",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 7
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_013_000009",
    "sentence": "永熙二年 ，除使持節、都督定州刺史、六州大都督。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "二年",
        "label": "TME",
